data.title: With the US having such a gun culture, why are they so uncompetitive in Olympic shooting?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 39): Our current Olympic shotgun team is pretty formidable.

Kimberly Rhodes, anyone? :-)

Historically, our shotgun shooters are the ones bringing in most of the Olympic shooting medals for the U.S.

Our rifle guys and gals are not too shabby, either, but not as good as the shotgun ...
